headline: Northern Trust Signs MoU with Universiti Brunei Darussalam to Foster Digital and Fintech Talent
summary: BANDAR SERI BEGAWAN, Brunei, September 24, 2025--Northern Trust and UBD agreed to work together on research and development initiatives in digital assets and other innovations in financial markets.
